"\n"
"You can view the payment information and the status of your order at\n"
"{url}\n"
"\n"
"Best regards,\n"
"Your {event} team"
msgstr ""
"Hola,\n"
"\n"
"no hem rebut el pagament complet de la vostra comanda per {event}.\n"
