#: base/models/settings.py:71
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Hi,\n"
"\n"
"we hope you’re happy with eventyay as your event’s CfP system.\n"
"These links may be helpful in the coming days and weeks:\n"
"\n"
"- Your event’s dashboard: {event_dashboard}\n"
"- A list of proposals: {event_submissions}\n"
"- Your schedule editor: {event_schedule}\n"
"\n"
"If there is anything you’re missing, please contact us via our website on "
"eventyay.com.\n"
msgstr ""
"Hola,\n"
"\n"
"esperem que estiguis satisfet amb eventyay com a sistema de CfP del teu "
"esdeveniment.\n"
"Aquests enllaços poden ser útils els propers dies i setmanes:\n"
"\n"
"- El tauler del teu esdeveniment: {event_dashboard}\n"
"- Una llista de propostes: {event_submissions}\n"
"- L'editor del teu programa: {event_schedule}\n"
"\n"
"Si et falta qualsevol cosa, si us plau contacta'ns a través del nostre lloc "
"web a eventyay.com.\n"

#: base/models/settings.py:90
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Hi,\n"
"\n"
"just writing you to let you know that your Call for Participation is now\n"
"closed. Here is a list of links that should be useful in the next days:\n"
"\n"
"- You’ll find a list of all your {submission_count} proposals here:\n"
"  {event_submissions}\n"
"- You can add reviewers here:\n"
"  {event_team}\n"
"- You can review proposals here:\n"
"  {event_review}\n"
"- And create your schedule here, once you have accepted proposals:\n"
"  {event_schedule}\n"
msgstr ""
"Hola,\n"
"\n"
"només t'escric per fer-te saber que la teva Convocatòria de Participació ja "
"és tancada. Aquí tens una llista d'enllaços que et poden ser útils els "
"pròxims dies:\n"
"\n"
"- Trobaràs una llista de totes les teves propostes de {submission_count} "
"aquí:\n"
"  {event_submissions}\n"
"- Pots afegir revisors aquí:\n"
"  {event_team}\n"
"- Pots revisar propostes aquí:\n"
"  {event_review}\n"
"- I crear el teu programa aquí, un cop hagis acceptat propostes:\n"
"  {event_schedule}\n"

#: base/models/settings.py:112
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Hi,\n"
"\n"
"congratulations, your event is over! Hopefully it went well. Here are some\n"
"statistics you might find interesting:\n"
"\n"
"- You had {submission_count} proposals,\n"
"- Of which you selected {talk_count} sessions.\n"
"- The reviewers wrote {review_count} reviews.\n"
"- You released {schedule_count} schedules in total.\n"
"- Over the course of the event, you sent {mail_count} mails.\n"
"\n"
"If there is anything you’re missing, please contact us via our website on "
"eventyay.com.\n"
msgstr ""
"Hola,\n"
"\n"
"felicitats, el teu esdeveniment s'ha acabat! Esperem que hagi anat bé. Aquí "
"tens algunes\n"
"estadístiques que potser et semblaran interessants:\n"
"\n"
"- Has tingut {submission_count} propostes,\n"
"- De les quals has seleccionat {talk_count} sessions.\n"
"- Els revisors han escrit {review_count} ressenyes.\n"
"- Has publicat {schedule_count} programes en total.\n"
"- Al llarg de l'esdeveniment, has enviat {mail_count} correus.\n"
"\n"
"Si et falta qualsevol cosa, si us plau contacta'ns a través del nostre lloc "
"web a eventyay.com.\n"

