#: cfp/flow.py:501
msgid "That’s it about your proposal! We now just need a way to contact you."
msgstr ""
"Això és tot sobre la teva proposta! Ara només necessitem una manera de "
"contactar amb tu."

#: cfp/flow.py:506
msgid ""
"To create your proposal, you need an account on this page. This not only "
"gives us a way to contact you, it also gives you the possibility to edit "
"your proposal or to view its current state."
msgstr ""
"Per crear la teva proposta, necessites un compte en aquesta pàgina. Això no "
"només ens dona una manera de contactar amb tu, també et dona la possibilitat "
"d'editar la teva proposta o de veure'n l'estat actual."

#: cfp/flow.py:549
#: eventyay_common/templates/eventyay_common/sessions/sessions.html:36
msgid "Profile"
msgstr "Perfil"

#: cfp/flow.py:553
msgid "Tell us something about yourself!"
msgstr "Explica'ns alguna cosa sobre tu!"

#: cfp/flow.py:558
msgid ""
"This information will be publicly displayed next to your session - you can "
"always edit for as long as proposals are still open."
msgstr ""
"Aquesta informació es mostrarà públicament al costat de la teva sessió – "
"sempre la pots editar mentre les propostes estiguin encara obertes."

#: cfp/phrases.py:7
msgid "Go to CfP"
msgstr "Ves a la CfP"

#: cfp/phrases.py:10
msgid ""
"If we know a user by this email address (who has not requested a password "
"reset in the last 24 hours), we will send you an email containing further "
"instructions. If you don’t see the email within the next minutes, check your "
"spam inbox!"
msgstr ""
"Si coneixem un usuari amb aquesta adreça de correu electrònic (que no hagi "
"sol·licitat un restabliment de contrasenya en les últimes 24 hores), "
"t'enviarem un correu electrònic amb més instruccions. Si no el veus en els "
"propers minuts, comprova la carpeta de correu brossa!"

#: cfp/phrases.py:14
msgid ""
"This link was not valid. Make sure you copied the complete URL from the "
"email and that the email is no more than 24 hours old."
msgstr ""
"Aquest enllaç no era vàlid. Assegura't que has copiat l'URL complet del "
"correu electrònic i que el correu no té més de 24 hores."

#: cfp/phrases.py:17
msgid "Awesome! You can now log in using your new password."
msgstr "Genial! Ara pots iniciar sessió amb la teva nova contrasenya."

#: cfp/phrases.py:19
msgid "Your proposal has been withdrawn."
msgstr "La vostra proposta ha estat cancel·lada."

#: cfp/phrases.py:21
msgid ""
"Your proposal can’t be withdrawn at this time – please contact us if you "
"need to withdraw your proposal!"
msgstr ""
"La teva proposta no es pot retirar en aquest moment – posa't en contacte amb "
"nosaltres si necessites retirar la teva proposta!"

#: cfp/phrases.py:23
msgid "Your session has been confirmed – we’re looking forward to seeing you!"
msgstr "Felicitats, la vostra proposta ha estat confirmada!"

#: cfp/phrases.py:24
msgid ""
"This proposal has already been confirmed – we’re looking forward to seeing "
"you!"
msgstr "Aquesta proposta ja ha estat confirmada – tenim ganes de veure't!"

#: cfp/phrases.py:26
msgid ""
"This proposal cannot be confirmed at this time – please contact us if you "
"think this is an error."
msgstr ""
"Aquesta proposta no es pot confirmar en aquest moment – posa't en contacte "
"amb nosaltres si creus que es tracta d'un error."

#: cfp/phrases.py:28
msgid "This proposal cannot be edited anymore."
msgstr "Aquesta proposta ja no es pot editar."

#: cfp/phrases.py:30 cfp/phrases.py:53
msgid "Speaker email"
msgstr "Correu electrònic del ponent"

#: cfp/phrases.py:31 cfp/phrases.py:54
#, python-brace-format
msgid "{speaker} invites you to join their session!"
msgstr "{speaker} et convida a unir-te a la seva sessió!"

#: cfp/phrases.py:33 cfp/phrases.py:56
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Hi!\n"
"\n"
"I’d like to invite you to be a speaker in the session\n"
"\n"
"  “{title}”\n"
"\n"
"at {event}. Please follow this link to join:\n"
"\n"
"  {url}\n"
"\n"
"I’m looking forward to it!\n"
"{speaker}"
msgstr ""
"Hola!\n"
"\n"
"M’agradaria convidar-te a ser ponent a la sessió\n"
"\n"
"  “{title}”\n"
"\n"
"a {event}. Si us plau, segueix aquest enllaç per unir-t’hi:\n"
"\n"
"  {url}\n"
"\n"
"En tinc moltes ganes!\n"
"{speaker}"

#: cfp/phrases.py:46
msgid "Please provide a valid email address."
msgstr "Si us plau, proporciona una adreça de correu electrònic vàlida."

#: cfp/phrases.py:47
msgid "The invitation was sent!"
msgstr "S’ha enviat la invitació!"

#: cfp/phrases.py:48
msgid "You are now part of this proposal! Please fill in your profile below."
msgstr ""
"Ara formes part d’aquesta proposta! Si us plau, omple el teu perfil a "
"continuació."

#: cfp/phrases.py:51
msgid ""
"We are experiencing difficulties when sending mails, but your session was "
"submitted successfully!"
msgstr ""
"Estem tenint dificultats per enviar correus electrònics, però la teva sessió "
"s’ha enviat correctament!"

#: cfp/phrases.py:69 orga/views/cfp.py:343
