#: control/templates/pretixcontrol/event/widget.html:17
msgid ""
"A widget allows you to embed your ticket shop directly into your event "
"website. This enables your visitors to purchase tickets instantly without "
"leaving your site."
msgstr ""
"Un widget et permet incrustar la teva botiga d'entrades directament al web "
"del teu esdeveniment. Això permet que els teus visitants comprin entrades a "
"l'instant sense sortir del teu lloc web."

#: control/templates/pretixcontrol/event/widget.html:23
msgid ""
"To embed the widget onto your website, simply copy the following code to the "
"<code>&lt;head&gt;</code> section of your website:"
msgstr ""
"Per incrustar el widget al teu lloc web, simplement copia el codi següent a "
