#: control/templates/pretixcontrol/shredder/download.html:5
#: control/templates/pretixcontrol/shredder/download.html:8
#: control/templates/pretixcontrol/shredder/index.html:5
#: control/templates/pretixcontrol/shredder/index.html:8
msgid "Data shredder"
msgstr "Destructora de dades"

#: control/templates/pretixcontrol/shredder/download.html:15
msgid "Step 1: Download data"
msgstr "Pas 1: Baixa les dades"

#: control/templates/pretixcontrol/shredder/download.html:17
msgid "(Optional) Step 1: Download data"
msgstr "(Opcional) Pas 1: Baixa les dades"

#: control/templates/pretixcontrol/shredder/download.html:20
msgid ""
"You are about to permanently delete data from the server, even though you "
"might be required to keep some of this data on file. You can therefore "
"download the following file and store it in a safe place:"
msgstr ""
"Estàs a punt d'eliminar permanentment dades del servidor, tot i que potser "
"estàs obligat a conservar-ne algunes. Per tant, pots baixar el fitxer "
"següent i desar-lo en un lloc segur:"

#: control/templates/pretixcontrol/shredder/download.html:29
msgid "Download data"
msgstr "Baixa les dades"

#: control/templates/pretixcontrol/shredder/download.html:34
msgid "Step 2: Confirm deletion"
msgstr "Pas 2: Confirma l'eliminació"

#: control/templates/pretixcontrol/shredder/download.html:36
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Please re-check that you are fully certain that you want to delete the "
"selected categories of data from the event <strong>%(event)s</strong>. To "
"confirm you really want this, please type out the event's short name "
"(\"%(slug)s\") here:"
msgstr ""
"Torna a comprovar que estàs completament segur que vols eliminar les "
"categories de dades seleccionades de l'esdeveniment <strong>%(event)s</"
"strong>. Per confirmar que realment ho vols, escriu aquí el nom curt de "
"l'esdeveniment (\"%(slug)s\"):"

#: control/templates/pretixcontrol/shredder/download.html:41
msgid "Event short name"
msgstr "Nom curt de l'esdeveniment"

#: control/templates/pretixcontrol/shredder/download.html:46
msgid "Step 3: Confirm download"
msgstr "Pas 3: Confirma la baixada"

#: control/templates/pretixcontrol/shredder/download.html:48
msgid ""
"In the downloaded file, there is a text file named \"CONFIRM_CODE.txt\" with "
"a six-character code. Please enter this code here to confirm that you "
"successfully downloaded the file."
msgstr ""
"Al fitxer descarregat hi ha un fitxer de text anomenat \"CONFIRM_CODE.txt\" "
"amb un codi de sis caràcters. Introdueix aquest codi aquí per confirmar que "
"has baixat el fitxer correctament."

#: control/templates/pretixcontrol/shredder/download.html:53
msgid "Confirmation code"
msgstr "Codi de confirmació"

#: control/templates/pretixcontrol/shredder/index.html:11
msgid ""
"This feature allows you to remove personal data from this event. You will "
"first select what kind of data you want to shred, then you are able to "
"download the affected data and after you confirmed the download, the data "
"will be removed from the server's database. The data might still exist in "
"backups for a limited period of time."
msgstr ""
"Aquesta funció et permet eliminar dades personals d'aquest esdeveniment. "
"Primer seleccionaràs quin tipus de dades vols destruir, després podràs "
"baixar les dades afectades i, un cop hagis confirmat la baixada, les dades "
"s'eliminaran de la base de dades del servidor. Les dades encara podrien "
"existir a les còpies de seguretat durant un període de temps limitat."

#: control/templates/pretixcontrol/shredder/index.html:18
msgid ""
"Using this will not remove the orders for your event, it just scrubs them of "
"data that can be linked to individual persons."
msgstr ""
"Fer ús d'això no eliminarà les comandes del teu esdeveniment, només "
"n'esborrarà les dades que es puguin vincular a persones individuals."

#: control/templates/pretixcontrol/shredder/index.html:26
msgid ""
"It is within your own responsibility to check if you are allowed to delete "
"the affected data in your legislation, e.g. for reasons of taxation. In many "
"countries, you need to keep some data in the live system in case of an audit."
msgstr ""
"És responsabilitat teva comprovar si la legislació aplicable et permet "
"eliminar les dades afectades, per exemple per motius fiscals. En molts "
"països, cal conservar algunes dades al sistema en producció en cas d'una "
"auditoria."

#: control/templates/pretixcontrol/shredder/index.html:32
msgid ""
"For most categories of data, you will be able to partially download the data "
"to store it offline. Some kinds of data (such as some payment information) "
"as well as historical log data cannot be downloaded at the moment."
msgstr ""
"Per a la majoria de categories de dades, podràs baixar parcialment les dades "
"per desar-les fora de línia. Alguns tipus de dades (com ara part de la "
"informació de pagament) així com les dades històriques de registre no es "
"poden baixar de moment."

#: control/templates/pretixcontrol/shredder/index.html:46
msgid "Data selection"
msgstr "Selecció de dades"

#: control/templates/pretixcontrol/shredder/index.html:63
msgid ""
"We recommend not to remove this data because you might need it in case of a "
"tax audit."
msgstr ""
"Recomanem no eliminar aquestes dades perquè les podries necessitar en cas "
"d'una auditoria fiscal."

