#: plugins/banktransfer/payment.py:35
msgid ""
"I have understood that people will pay the ticket price directly to my bank "
"account and eventyay cannot automatically know what payments arrived. "
"Therefore, I will either mark payments as complete manually, or regularly "
"import a digital bank statement in order to give eventyay the required "
"information."
msgstr ""
"He entès que la gent pagarà el preu de l'entrada directament al meu compte "
"bancari i que eventyay no pot saber automàticament quins pagaments han "
"arribat. Per tant, marcaré els pagaments com a completats manualment o "
"importaré regularment un extracte bancari digital per tal de proporcionar a "
"eventyay la informació necessària."

