"transfer payment. If you have lots of international customers, they might "
"need your full address and your bank's full address."
msgstr ""
"Inclou tota la resta que els teus clients puguin necessitar per enviar-te un "
"pagament per transferència bancària. Si tens molts clients internacionals, "
"potser necessitaran la teva adreça completa i l'adreça completa del teu banc."

#: plugins/banktransfer/payment.py:121
