#: plugins/banktransfer/payment.py:189
msgid ""
"Put one IBAN or IBAN prefix per line. The system will not attempt to send "
"refunds to any of these IBANs. Useful e.g. if you receive a lot of "
"\"forwarded payments\" by a third-party payment provider. You can also list "
"country codes such as \"GB\" if you never want to send refunds to IBANs from "
"a specific country."
msgstr ""
"Posa un IBAN o un prefix d'IBAN per línia. El sistema no intentarà enviar "
"reemborsaments a cap d'aquests IBAN. És útil, per exemple, si reps molts "
"\"pagaments reenviats\" per un proveïdor de pagaments de tercers. També pots "
"indicar codis de país com ara \"GB\" si no vols mai enviar reemborsaments a "
"IBAN d'un país específic."

