msgid "You chose an invalid cancellation fee."
msgstr "Heu triat una taxa de cancel·lació no vàlida."

#: presale/views/order.py:1079
msgid "Canceled by customer"
msgstr "Cancel·lat pel client"

#: presale/views/order.py:1095
msgid "The cancellation has been requested."
msgstr "S'ha demanat la cancel·lació."

#: presale/views/order.py:1150
msgid "Ticket download is not (yet) enabled for this order."
msgstr ""
"La baixada de tiquets encara no ha estat habilitada per a aquesta comanda."

#: presale/views/order.py:1159
msgid "Please click the link we sent you via email to download your tickets."
msgstr ""
"Cliqueu a l'enllaç que us hem enviat per correu electrònic per tal de "
"descarregar les vostres entrades."

#: presale/views/order.py:1331
msgid "You cannot change this order."
msgstr "No podeu modificar aquesta comanda."

#: presale/views/order.py:1445
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"The order has been changed. You can now proceed by paying the open amount of "
"{amount}."
msgstr ""
"S'ha modificat la comanda. Ara pots continuar pagant l'import pendent de "
"{amount}."

#: presale/views/user.py:27
msgid "We had difficulties processing your input."
msgstr "Hem tingut dificultats per processar la teva entrada."

#: presale/views/user.py:40
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"If the email address you entered is valid and associated with a ticket, we "
"have already sent you an email with a link to your ticket in the past "
"{number} hours. If the email did not arrive, please your check spam folder "
"and also double check that you used the correct email address."
msgstr ""
"Si l'adreça electrònica que has introduït és vàlida i està associada a una "
"entrada, ja t'hem enviat un correu electrònic amb un enllaç a la teva "
"entrada durant les últimes {number} hores. Si el correu no ha arribat, "
"comprova la carpeta de correu brossa i també verifica que has utilitzat "
"l'adreça electrònica correcta."

#: presale/views/user.py:55
#, python-brace-format
msgid "Your orders for {}"
msgstr "Les vostres comandes per a {}"

#: presale/views/user.py:72
msgid "We have trouble sending emails right now, please check back later."
msgstr ""
"Tenim problemes enviant correus electrònics ara mateix. Si us plau, proveu-"
"ho més tard."

#: presale/views/user.py:78
msgid ""
"If there were any orders by this user, they will receive an email with their "
"order codes."
msgstr ""
"Si aquest usuari ha fet alguna comanda, rebrà un correu electrònic amb els "
"codis de les seves comandes."

#: presale/views/waiting.py:89
msgid "Waiting lists are disabled for this event."
msgstr "Les llistes d'espera no estan habilitades per a aquest esdeveniment."

#: presale/views/waiting.py:93
msgid "We could not identify the product you selected."
msgstr "No podem identificar el producte que heu seleccionat."

#: presale/views/waiting.py:97
msgid "The waiting list is disabled for this product."
msgstr "La llista d'espera està desactivada per a aquest producte."

#: presale/views/waiting.py:124
msgid ""
"You cannot add yourself to the waiting list as this product is currently "
"available."
msgstr ""
"No us podeu afegir a la llista d'espera perquè aquest producte encara està "
"disponible."

#: presale/views/waiting.py:131
msgid ""
"We've added you to the waiting list. You will receive an email as soon as "
"tickets get available again."
msgstr ""
"Us hem afegit a la llista d'espera. Rebreu un correu electrònic quan hi "
"torni a haver tiquets disponibles."

