msgstr "iCal (les teves sessions marcades amb estrella)"

#: schedule/forms.py:20
msgid ""
"Please click and drag to mark your availability during the conference with "
"green blocks. We will try to schedule your slot during these times. You can "
"click a block twice to remove it."
msgstr ""
"Fes clic i arrossega per marcar la teva disponibilitat durant la conferència "
"amb blocs verds. Intentarem programar el teu espai en aquestes franges. Pots "
"fer doble clic en un bloc per eliminar-lo."

#: schedule/forms.py:75
#, python-brace-format
msgid "Please note that all times are in the event timezone, {tz}."
msgstr ""
"Tingues en compte que totes les hores són a la zona horària de "
"l'esdeveniment, {tz}."

#: schedule/forms.py:80
msgid ""
"If you set room availabilities, speakers will only be able to set their "
"availability for when any room is available."
msgstr ""
"Si establiu disponibilitats de sala, els ponents només podran establir la "
"seva disponibilitat per als moments en què hi hagi alguna sala disponible."

#: schedule/forms.py:110
msgid "The submitted availability does not comply with the required format."
msgstr "La disponibilitat enviada no compleix el format requerit."

#: schedule/forms.py:124
msgid "The submitted availability contains an invalid date."
msgstr "La disponibilitat enviada conté una data no vàlida."

#: schedule/forms.py:139
msgid "Please fill in your availability!"
msgstr "Si us plau, empleneu la vostra disponibilitat!"

#: schedule/forms.py:196
msgid "Room I"
msgstr "Sala I"

#: schedule/forms.py:198
msgid ""
"Description, e.g.: Our main meeting place, Room I, enter from the right."
msgstr ""
"Descripció, p. ex.: El nostre lloc principal de reunió, Sala I, entreu per "
"la dreta."

#: schedule/forms.py:201
msgid "Information for speakers, e.g.: Projector has only HDMI input."
msgstr ""
"Informació per als ponents, p. ex.: El projector només té entrada HDMI."

